This rule covers generation of data assets for "FTBKingdoms". Data generation is preferred. [3, 9, 13]

**Main Data Generator Setup:** Subscribe to `GatherDataEvent`. `DataGenerator generator = event.getGenerator(); ... generator.addProvider(event.includeClient(), new MyBlockStateProvider(packOutput, FTBKingdoms.MOD_ID, existingFileHelper));` [13]
**Provider Types:** `BlockStateProvider`, `ItemModelProvider`, `LanguageProvider`, `SoundDefinitionsProvider`, `RecipeProvider`, `LootTableProvider`, `TagsProvider`. [13]
**Location:** `datagen` sub-package.
**Running:** `runData` Gradle task. [13]

**Data Generation for "FTBKingdoms":**
*   **Blocks:** Treasury block, Jail Wall/Door/Controller blocks.
*   **Items:** Claim tool, Siege components, keys.
*   **LanguageProvider:** All UI text, names, messages for "FTBKingdoms".

*   **SoundDefinitionsProvider:** Custom sounds.